comments: Brown (BOS) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Walker (BOS) makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) lower body and affects his jump shot attempt.
Kornet (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Richardson's (DAL) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the screen.
Brunson (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during Walker's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Brunson (DAL) moves through the marginal leg to leg contact with Walker (BOS) as he changes directions during his driving shot attempt. Walker swipes down and avoids making contact to Walker's arm.
Smart (BOS) and Richardson (DAL) mutually engage in marginal contact during the inbound.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Kleber (DAL).
Tatum (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position as he steals the ball from Richardson (DAL).
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position by absorbing the contact from Tatum (BOS) during the driving shot attempt.
As Smart (BOS) moves naturally toward the rebound, incidental body contact occurs with Doncic (DAL).
Fournier (BOS) commits a take foul on Brunson (DAL).
Doncic (DAL) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) makes contact to Smart's (BOS) arm that affects his ability to control the rebound.
Correctly whistled free throw violation on Smart (BOS).
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Brunson (DAL).
